{"tid":1878294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自從反送中同肺炎爆發後, 香港舒服左好多","createTime":"2020-02-13T13:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T15:29:02.000Z","uid":41458,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2548aee7f13bdc4f93989955701ac0e6db5682","tid":1878294,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"1. 支那人大量減少, 街道寬落好多, 行得舒服<br />\n2. 街道更乾淨整潔, 冇左支那人周圍吐啖掉垃圾屙屎屙尿<br />\n3. 餐廳食野唔洗點排隊<br />\n4. 商場人流少. 行得好舒服<br />\n5. 搭車又快左, 冇咁迫<br />\n6. 有我work from home, 工時短左好多, 唔會OT, 同屋企人相處時間多左<br />\n7. 整體香港既通漲暫停左, 新年D 鋪都唔會再加價, 甚至有D係減價<br />\n8. 公路好少塞車, 泊車大把位<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實香港可以好舒服, 最緊要就係趕絕支那狗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a4b0b3cb98025218637655f9f63686c01644031c","tid":1878294,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9f491aa3cf066cbeaf0ef866a2594677c70b0c","tid":1878294,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99073b864ac7ee959711478df55624368ea69fe","tid":1878294,"uid":7270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"285ab3e0a6acf5ebc0e9e7419fcd55506e62f572","tid":1878294,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"如果可以繼續少人同舒服 <br />\n雖然已經窮 願意再窮都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be3b350cdb389c12e883cf25a86a61c012acfea","tid":1878294,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"黎黎去去都係武肺<br />\n反送中咪又係咁多支那人<img src